template
    h2 first step? log in
    form(submit.bind="login()" autocomplete="off")
        .mdc-form-field.mdc-text-field.mdc-text-field--outlined.mdc-text-field--with-trailing-icon.mdc-text-field--upgraded
            input#email.mdc-text-field__input(type='email' value.bind="user.email" required)
            label.mdc-text-field__label(for='email') Email
            i.material-icons.mdc-text-field__icon(tabindex='0') face
            .mdc-text-field__outline.mdc-ripple-upgraded
                svg
                    path.mdc-text-field__outline-path
            .mdc-text-field__idle-outline
        .mdc-form-field.mdc-text-field.mdc-text-field--outlined.mdc-text-field--with-trailing-icon.mdc-text-field--upgraded
            input#password.mdc-text-field__input(type='password' value.bind="user.password" required)
            label.mdc-text-field__label(for='password') Password
            i.material-icons.mdc-text-field__icon(tabindex='0') lock
            .mdc-text-field__outline.mdc-ripple-upgraded
                svg
                    path.mdc-text-field__outline-path
            .mdc-text-field__idle-outline
        div.sunshower-button-holder
            button(type="submit")
                | get going
    p if you're not quite there yet,
        | #{' '}
        a(click.delegate="signup()") step zero is to sign up
    p heck, go
        | #{' '}
        a read the docs
        |  -- we'll wait